mr.sql: SELECT DISTINCT T1.FLIGHT_ID FROM FLIGHT AS T1 JOIN DAYS AS T2 ON T1.FLIGHT_DAYS = T2.DAYS_CODE JOIN AIRPORT_SERVICE AS T3 ON T1.TO_AIRPORT = T3.AIRPORT_CODE JOIN AIRPORT_SERVICE AS T4 ON T1.FROM_AIRPORT = T4.AIRPORT_CODE JOIN FLIGHT_FARE AS T5 ON T1.FLIGHT_ID = T5.FLIGHT_ID JOIN CITY AS T6 ON T6.CITY_CODE = T3.CITY_CODE JOIN CITY AS T7 ON T7.CITY_CODE = T4.CITY_CODE JOIN FARE AS T8 ON T5.FARE_ID = T8.FARE_ID WHERE ( ( ( ( ( ( T1.ARRIVAL_TIME < T1.DEPARTURE_TIME ) AND T2.DAY_NAME = "MONDAY" ) OR ( T2.DAY_NAME = "TUESDAY" AND NOT ( T1.ARRIVAL_TIME < T1.DEPARTURE_TIME ) ) ) AND T1.ARRIVAL_TIME > 1200 ) AND T6.CITY_NAME = "PHILADELPHIA" ) AND T7.CITY_NAME = "BOSTON" ) AND T8.ONE_DIRECTION_COST = ( SELECT T8.ONE_DIRECTION_COST FROM FLIGHT AS T1 JOIN DAYS AS T2 ON T1.FLIGHT_DAYS = T2.DAYS_CODE JOIN AIRPORT_SERVICE AS T3 ON T1.TO_AIRPORT = T3.AIRPORT_CODE JOIN FLIGHT_FARE AS T4 ON T1.FLIGHT_ID = T4.FLIGHT_ID JOIN AIRPORT_SERVICE AS T5 ON T1.FROM_AIRPORT = T5.AIRPORT_CODE JOIN CITY AS T6 ON T6.CITY_CODE = T3.CITY_CODE JOIN CITY AS T7 ON T7.CITY_CODE = T5.CITY_CODE JOIN FARE AS T8 ON T4.FARE_ID = T8.FARE_ID WHERE ( ( ( ( ( T1.ARRIVAL_TIME < T1.DEPARTURE_TIME ) AND T2.DAY_NAME = "MONDAY" ) OR ( T2.DAY_NAME = "TUESDAY" AND NOT ( T1.ARRIVAL_TIME < T1.DEPARTURE_TIME ) ) ) AND T1.ARRIVAL_TIME > 1200 ) AND T6.CITY_NAME = "PHILADELPHIA" ) AND T7.CITY_NAME = "BOSTON" AND T8.ROUND_TRIP_REQUIRED = "NO" ORDER BY T8.ONE_DIRECTION_COST LIMIT 1) AND T8.ROUND_TRIP_REQUIRED = "NO";
